translations: 人造奶油，人造奶酪；液态牛油

sentences.sentence: All three units of the gear are equipped oleo pneumatic shock absorbers.
sentences.translation: 全部三个起落架单元安装双腔油气减震器。

sentences.sentence: When closing the bridge two Oleo buffers are provided in addition to the elastomeric bearings.
sentences.translation: 当桥梁通道关闭时，两个油压缓冲装置提供除了弹性轴承外的支撑。

sentences.sentence: The imports and exports of oleo chemical-related products by countries are related respectively.
sentences.translation: 对各国油脂化学品及相关产品的进出口状况进行了分述。
